                            Appendum for V1.3
                           ===================
This release has been made to inform users that the game is available through
Vulcan Software. It is also to tell users that the problems with this demo
do not occur in the commercial game.

Version 1.3 over Version 1.2
============================
- Breed has now been compiled to be AGA friendly.
- The sounds from the war screen are less crappy.
- Cargo/Shield/Weapon updates are now saved.
- Alien casualties now register on their planet.
- Aliens start interacting sooner.
- Aliens are now more agressive if provoked.

Please Note
===========
1. You can't colonise other planets (that means you can't have more than
   one planet you are managing). In the registered version you can
   claim uninhabited planets.
2. You CAN remove road by pressing the right mouse button when laying road.

Thanks to everyone for their help, bug notifications, advice and compliments.


